name: Choc Hummus With Grapes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Soak sultanas in 2 tbs hot water until soft. Place drained chickpeas in a food processor and process with cacao powder, vanilla extract and sultanas until smooth.
Serve with green grapes. Leftover hummus can be frozen but the texture will be softer once thawed.
